{"tid":580290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[GDP來了][估省份]機場天花塌板　嚇親候機乘客　官方：太大風","createTime":"2018-03-04T11:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T11:37:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6967cb5c128059802b6993e1d0dc09121447cc85","tid":580290,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:35:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B1%9F%E8%A5%BF%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%A4%A9%E8%8A%B1%E5%A1%8C%E6%9D%BF-%E5%9A%87%E8%A6%AA%E5%80%99%E6%A9%9F%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9-%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%A7%E9%A2%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%25A1%258C%25E6%259D%25BF-%25E5%259A%2587%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%2580%2599%25E6%25A9%259F%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A2%25A8%2F&d=iQJTIZX%2BEOMcx2Zwu%2FiUAi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ef650cf7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B1%259F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%25A1%258C%25E6%259D%25BF-%25E5%259A%2587%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E5%2580%2599%25E6%25A9%259F%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A2%25A8%2F&h=8fd3db54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B1%9F%E8%A5%BF%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%A4%A9%E8%8A%B1%E5%A1%8C%E6%9D%BF-%E5%9A%87%E8%A6%AA%E5%80%99%E6%A9%9F%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9-%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%A7%E9%A2%A8/</a><br />\n<br />\n江西南昌昌北機場屋頂今午天花有大量條板塌落，幸好無人傷亡，誇張景象被網民拍下放到網上，不少目睹景象的現場候機人士驚叫。機場事後解釋，是因為大風的緣故。<br />\n<br />\n江西省機場集團公司官方微博公布，今午3時半，南昌昌北國際機場突遇大風天氣，陣風超30米/秒，T2航站樓入口區域部分屋簷裝飾材料被大風吹下，現場無人員傷亡，機場已對航站樓出發廳出入口進行管控，進出港旅客均改為由到達廳進入航站樓。<br />\n<br />\n大風期間有兩個進港航班要轉到其他機場降落，一個進港航班返航，目前南昌機場已恢復航班運行保障。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，南昌氣象台、中央氣象台等官方微博均轉發視頻，並提及昌北機場測到的最大雷雨大風為37米/秒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OXqG_i-vTt8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOXqG_i-vTt8&d=iQJTIZX%2BEOMcx2Zwu%2FiUAi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ae8dc0b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OXqG_i-vTt8</a>"},{"pid":"95dac52bc04948975f0189659d093eeb64b151ab","tid":580290,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:37:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}